string-array.name: people_desc
string-array.item: A 15 year old developer - the maker of this app! No credit is required for any of his wallpapers.
A high school student who makes awesome free wallpapers that anyone can use as long as they give credit.
A google plus user who makes icons for his icon pack Colorcons in his spare time and is currently making an amazing new icon for this app! (not finished yet) He also donated a few wallpapers.

An enthusiastic material-design lover from Slovenia that gave all his wallpapers (there\'s a lot) to this app. He posts them (and more) to his blog on blogspot. He also made (most of) the images used in the tutorial.
A young designer and developer that likes to make wallpapers in his free time.
A designer that loves making minimal and material design wallpapers.
An android lover that proudly roots and flashes all his devices.
